surf_greensway


Surf info:
linear
tier 2
2 checkpoints.
3500 maxvel

Made for the 2020 KSF Spring Skill Surf Mapping Contest

The theme is around green candy forest with chocolate rivers 
The given theme keywords were "sunnyhappylove",  and I went with a sunny cliffy forest environment where sweets are found in nature itself.

The surf is symmetrical in the beginning and then joins back again in one route until the end. The map is about 50 secs long +- 10 secs depending on speed. There are also a few ramps you can skip, for higher speed surfers.

So yeah. I had quite a alot of fun making this map, and the custom stuff and all, and I hope people do too playing it )
